{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Improve awareness of Clare\u2019s Law and require earlier right to know disclosures",
        "additional_details": "Many victims only learn of a partner\u2019s abusive history after serious harm has already occurred. Earlier disclosure and more awareness could help people make safer choices sooner. Posters and adverts with Clare\u2019s Law details in schools, workplaces and public spaces could help people recognise risk, understand coercive control and stalking, and know where to seek help.",
        "background": "Require earlier Clare\u2019s Law right to know disclosures from the police where there is clear risk, and improve awareness of right to ask through schools, workplaces and public information so more people know the scheme exists and can seek help sooner.",
